":"2021-02-04T07:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29debbe38c80cd77a032726b9270383399a06249","tid":2394390,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:38:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d55791c0f71d0085ece18b3c4a357084ac5edbb","tid":2394390,"uid":264158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T22:25:06.000Z","msg":"&quot;被要求「二選一」申報是加拿大或中國公民&quot;<br />\n<br />\n好小事姐 申報加拿大咪得囉"},{"pid":"7996d42081dfdde5ed480df4499c0bb932057820","tid":2394390,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d55791c0f71d0085ece18b3c4a357084ac5edbb","tid":2394390,"uid":264158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T22:25:06.000Z","msg":"&quot;被要求「二選一」申報是加拿大或中國公民&quot;<br />\n<br />\n好小事姐 申報加拿大咪得囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T22:56:43.000Z","msg":"你sure 佢係俾你揀而唔係你首先是中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4f4e94e3c998bbbaf469971f7692106b967c42","tid":2394390,"uid":389613,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T23:12:03.000Z","msg":"成日有人講國際慣例，講多次 乜 96 年就有，講多次廢事有人懶醒：<br />\n<br />\nE家係香港入境處響 1/31 偷偷地改左指引<br />\n導致全世界政府無左權利保護/支持佢地響香港既僑胞<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">講多 N 次唔關國際慣例事，係入境處改左指引</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">1/31之前應該幫到你但1/31之後唔得</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">本來有既權利突然無左呀！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個世界有樣野叫 abuse of right (濫用權力)。而家問題係入境處 1/31 改左個指引可以濫用呢個權力，英國同加拿大政府先要發警告。 <br />\n<br />\n<ins><em>唔好再講乜 day 1 就係咁。 <br />\n<br />\n係 2021 年 1 月 31 日開始條界線比港共改左 </em></ins>"},{"pid":"c7da776fd058ae3a90d3e846b33c6b0e5f57df1b","tid":2394390,"uid":389613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T23:14:00.000Z","msg":"加拿大指香港拒絕領事館為雙重國籍被拘人士提供協助<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574095-20210204.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574095-20210204.htm&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=8831b039\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574095-20210204.htm&h=2c70ad79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574095-20210204.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n英國稱未必能向英中雙重國籍人士提供領事協助<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574821-20210209.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574821-20210209.htm&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=987358dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574821-20210209.htm&h=300bf18c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574821-20210209.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n澳洲政府更新對香港的旅遊提示，提醒香港在國安法生效後，不再承認雙重國籍。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hkcnews_com/status/1359381477037801472\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkcnews_com%2Fstatus%2F1359381477037801472&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=d6ed7d3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkcnews_com%2Fstatus%2F1359381477037801472&h=0195c1b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hkcnews_com/status/1359381477037801472</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢疫情：英國撤僑飛機「無法按原計劃起飛」<br />\n<blockquote>中國不承認雙重國籍，但英國允許雙重國籍的存在。<span class=\"red\">中國不允許雙重國籍護照持有人通過撤僑通道離開中國。</span>來自約克的弗朗西斯（Natalie Francis）說，<span class=\"red\">她被告知必須將三歲的兒子留在中國，因為兒子有中國護照。</span>她說：「接到電話時，我無語了。」</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/uk-51306996\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fuk-51306996&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=7ba64050\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fuk-51306996&h=469e89c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/uk-51306996</a>"},{"pid":"ba5c297e97d32471874f4c5ef6dca876f2bc2f6e","tid":2394390,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d55791c0f71d0085ece18b3c4a357084ac5edbb","tid":2394390,"uid":264158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T22:25:06.000Z","msg":"&quot;被要求「二選一」申報是加拿大或中國公民&quot;<br />\n<br />\n好小事姐 申報加拿大咪得囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:01:59.000Z","msg":"刑滿之後要佢逐出境?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45df22feda23eed0e8d71e30f9c95268bb3d442e","tid":2394390,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d55791c0f71d0085ece18b3c4a357084ac5edbb","tid":2394390,"uid":264158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T22:25:06.000Z","msg":"&quot;被要求「二選一」申報是加拿大或中國公民&quot;<br />\n<br />\n好小事姐 申報加拿大咪得囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:05:00.000Z","msg":"你sure申報左唔會比人酷刑？<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">𧝁雅達</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3071b1ba2713d0f22f9269322211ed3b4f7cb007","tid":2394390,"uid":264158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7996d42081dfdde5ed480df4499c0bb932057820","tid":2394390,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d55791c0f71d0085ece18b3c4a357084ac5edbb","tid":2394390,"uid":264158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T22:25:06.000Z","msg":"&quot;被要求「二選一」申報是加拿大或中國公民&quot;<br />\n<br />\n好小事姐 申報加拿大咪得囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T22:56:43.000Z","msg":"你sure 佢係俾你揀而唔係你首先是中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:20:31.000Z","msg":"佢咁寫我咁睇啦 佢冇話叫佢放棄加籍"}]}